{"tid":586952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個肥絲死左，仲有千千萬萬個肥絲","createTime":"2018-03-10T04:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T05:54:26.000Z","uid":149991,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"020d1ce748adc05c5c18ff5f6f9d4b4a2c77aa6a","tid":586952,"uid":149991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"其實近排大家有冇發現，佢雖然好煩！<br />\n但反肥絲嘅大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而令佢成功咗&hellip;<br />\n佢即使死，無論係反佢嘅你地，定係支持佢幫佢繼續衝出黎「死埋右？」嘅人，佢已經令你地銘記於心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n他朝一日佢真係人都死撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，都永遠有班連登仔記住佢&hellip;同佢個「左右」&hellip;仲有佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （係啊，你地其實係一群老襟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n我冇話支唔支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，只係覺得作為一個花生群，佢一直出黎受撚好好笑~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係一個想有言論自由嘅地方真係兩邊都冇錯，但肥絲真係成功「左」，不過未成「右」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3c7ae315738ba47cec58e736e61894f45c1fec","tid":586952,"uid":62424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"肥絲 我屌你老母"},{"pid":"8712ec0c19386fee972136ae5453f3aa04a22214","tid":586952,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c96c03536eb99637efdeffb9d1168a926821e0ab","tid":586952,"uid":80011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"咪多得有人你呢啲人理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就block咗佢 不聞不問不正評不負評<br />\n你比幾千個負評佢佢咪又係開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班小學雞係度回佢評佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍唔撚住屌醒你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid